Purpose of the Web Application
The purpose of this web application is to provide a simple platform for practicing English communication skills. It allows users to view daily prompts, attempt small grammar quizzes, and track their progress. The application is designed to help students improve their English fluency and confidence, especially for campus placement interviews. By using a clean interface and easy navigation, this project also demonstrates teamwork, GitHub collaboration, and deployment skills.


